description:
I don't know who they are.
They're just people in a magazines I read.
They don't know who I am either.

I'm planning to release a book after minting about 100 works.
It will be delivered free of charge to the NFT owner.
And we are going to airdrop the NFT of the next FPF collection.

I'll let you know if there's any change. Thank you.


*only sell one piece per piece.
*The series continues to run.
name: Portraits of Unknown People
